{"tid":975583,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"個腦入面好似打交咁，好矛盾","createTime":"2019-01-09T18:05:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-10T02:10:54.000Z","uid":191476,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9d3628405f7d630d7f99dca3aa85c83991f94b51","tid":975583,"uid":191476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T18:05:20.000Z","msg":"由細到大都好想可以出人頭地，有一番作為<br />\n但現實係對自己好冇自信，好似乜都做唔好<br />\n根本自己都覺得自己好廢<br />\n<br />\n最廢就係明知自己有問題都唔肯努力改變<br />\n<br />\n好似讀書咁，明知要努力先可以有好成績<br />\n但我「覺得」努力咗都係冇結果<br />\n所以任由自己hea讀<br />\n雖然成績唔算太差，但我內心總相信如果有努力一定會更好（呢種諗法連自己都想俾膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n到今時今日都未揾到自己想做嘅方向，又冇一樣嘢特別突出<br />\n但我只係知自己唔甘心做個打工仔<br />\n所以夜闌人靜就會諗下可以做啲咩有意義又揾到錢嘅嘢<br />\n結果係諗到啲嘢，但冇咁嘅能力去實行<br />\n無論係知識定係人脈<br />\n然後又唔知要喺邊度入手開始準備<br />\n於是之後繼續過好冇人生意義的生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91a1a7ee5dece9d128703dea941645a032328fd5","tid":975583,"uid":90646,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T18:06:42.000Z","msg":"Woo 無心睡眠"},{"pid":"74bf18328ccb304c2a9bfa921642f569b2cbd9d0","tid":975583,"uid":191476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91a1a7ee5dece9d128703dea941645a032328fd5","tid":975583,"uid":90646,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T18:06:42.000Z","msg":"Woo 無心睡眠"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T18:07:27.000Z","msg":"你都係呀"},{"pid":"99215707e1a4096c3ec1a9f0a2b7f4c312bae22a","tid":975583,"uid":90646,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T18:07:29.000Z","msg":"認真小小覆 我成日都咁諗 但覺得自己無力去跳出舒適圈"},{"pid":"5fb7caad2040ab84bb654b80b836b444f7b6ccfe","tid":975583,"uid":140357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d3628405f7d630d7f99dca3aa85c83991f94b51","tid":975583,"